text:
Part of the confusion perhaps comes from a missing element in these two binary variables: present/future + thinking/linking. I'm not suggesting we should have four channels, just pinpointing where the confusion comes from to look for better solutions.
```if isAboutFuture { 
    if hasLink { 
        #linking-together 
    } 
    else { 
        #thinking-together 
    } 
} else { 
    #present-company 
}```

